task.summary: Started to setup Project as a SpringBootApplication

--- Added --- LagerhausRESTController for REST-Requests LagerhausDataService for Translation between DTOs, DataObjects and Resources LagerhausManager for Request to Database LagerhausBadRequestException for throwing in case of impossible conversion in LagerhausDataService
--- Added --- Data objects for internal representation
--- Added --- (initial version) DTO and Resource objects for external representation

--- Added --- Method getAllLagerhaus to RESTController, DataService and LagerhausManager DatabaseManager and StoredProcedure for connection to the Database Exceptions --- Updated --- DTO and Resources were combined

--- Added --- CollumnsSingleton for Database-Access --- Updated --- new Methods added to RESTController and DataService REMOVED calls to DatabaseManager from LagerhausManager -> swapping to JPA for DB-Calls

--- Updated --- pom.xml -> changed dependencies LagerhausDataService -> implemented ValidityChecks and Conversions LagerhausManager -> changed temporary Lieferung Creation LagerhausRESTController -> changed RequestMapping, shortened Methods

--- Added --- Delivery, DeliveryRepository, application.properties -> for JPA usage
--- Updated --- LagerhausManager -> for JPA usage pom.xml -> for JPA usage and for maven-builds
--- Added --- Database POJOs and Repositories --- Updated --- Moved DeliveryRepository, Added Constructors to POJOs, Changed username for DB

--- Added --- FullHarvestMonth, FullMaturityLevel for combining the Tables for DTOs --- Updated --- Changed DataService and Manager for JPA-Support, Changed insertLieferung in RESTController for auto-generated IDs
--- Updated --- Changed Weight of Delivery to double
--- Updated --- Fixed bugs caused by naming and naming-strategy Added @Repository annotation to repositories Changed methods to return null, if no object was found
--- Updated --- Removed unused Methods from DataService and Manager
--- Updated --- removed unused classes removed unused bean from AppConfiguration

--- Added --- LagerhausResourceNotFoundException for better feedback in validity-checks
--- Updated --- databasePOJOs, LieferungResourceDTO -> removed commented code LagerhausDataService -> added validity-checks LagerhausManager -> update returns null if not found (for validity-checks)
--- Removed --- Unused Exceptions
